## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e510c-191"><xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A>方法可讓您撰寫程式碼，將特定類型指派給類型參數的泛型方法定義，因此建立<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>物件，表示特定的建構的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-191">The <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> method allows you to write code that assigns specific types to the type parameters of a generic method definition, thus creating a <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> object that represents a particular constructed method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e510c-192">如果<xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.ContainsGenericParameters%2A>屬性的<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>物件會傳回`true`，您可以使用它來叫用方法，或建立叫用方法的委派。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-192">If the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.ContainsGenericParameters%2A> property of this <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> object returns `true`, you can use it to invoke the method or to create a delegate to invoke the method.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e510c-193">方法所建構<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A>方法可以開啟，也就是某些其類型引數可以是封閉式泛型類型的型別參數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-193">Methods constructed with the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> method can be open, that is, some of their type arguments can be type parameters of enclosing generic types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e510c-194">當您產生動態組件時，您可以使用這類開放的建構的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-194">You might use such open constructed methods when you generate dynamic assemblies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e510c-195">例如，請考慮下列 C#、 Visual Basic 和 c + + 程式碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-195">For example, consider the following C#, Visual Basic, and C++ code.</span></span>  
  
```  
class C  
{  
    T N<T,U>(T t, U u) {...}  
    public V M<V>(V v)  
    {  
        return N<V,int>(v, 42);  
    }  
}  
  
Class C  
    Public Function N(Of T,U)(ByVal ta As T, ByVal ua As U) As T  
        ...  
    End Function  
    Public Function M(Of V)(ByVal va As V ) As V  
        Return N(Of V, Integer)(va, 42)  
    End Function  
End Class  
  
ref class C  
{  
private:  
    generic <typename T, typename U> T N(T t, U u) {...}  
public:  
    generic <typename V> V M(V v)  
    {  
        return N<V, int>(v, 42);  
    }  
};  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e510c-196">方法主體`M`包含方法的呼叫`N`，指定的型別參數`M`並輸入<xref:System.Int32>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-196">The method body of `M` contains a call to method `N`, specifying the type parameter of `M` and the type <xref:System.Int32>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e510c-197"><xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.IsGenericMethodDefinition%2A>屬性會傳回`false`方法`N<V,int>`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-197">The <xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.IsGenericMethodDefinition%2A> property returns `false` for method `N<V,int>`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e510c-198"><xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.ContainsGenericParameters%2A>屬性會傳回`true`，因此方法`N<V,int>`無法叫用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-198">The <xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.ContainsGenericParameters%2A> property returns `true`, so method `N<V,int>` cannot be invoked.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e510c-199">如需泛型的方法特定的恆成立條件，請參閱<xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.IsGenericMethod%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-199">For a list of the invariant conditions for terms specific to generic methods, see the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.IsGenericMethod%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e510c-200">如需泛型反映中所使用的其他詞彙的非變異條件的清單，請參閱<xref:System.Type.IsGenericType%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-200">For a list of the invariant conditions for other terms used in generic reflection, see the <xref:System.Type.IsGenericType%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e510c-201">下列程式碼範例示範的屬性和方法<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>支援泛型方法的檢查。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-201">The following code example demonstrates the properties and methods of <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> that support the examination of generic methods.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e510c-202">此範例會執行下列作業：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-202">The example does the following:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="e510c-203">定義具有泛型方法的類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-203">Defines a class that has a generic method.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="e510c-204">建立<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>，代表泛型方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-204">Creates a <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> that represents the generic method.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="e510c-205">會顯示泛型方法定義的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-205">Displays properties of the generic method definition.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="e510c-206">指派類型的型別參數的引數<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>，並叫用產生的建構泛型方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-206">Assigns type arguments to the type parameters of the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>, and invokes the resulting constructed generic method.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="e510c-207">顯示屬性的建構泛型方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-207">Displays properties of the constructed generic method.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="e510c-208">擷取建構方法的泛型方法定義，並將其比較的原始定義。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e510c-208">Retrieves the generic method definition from the constructed method and compares it to the original definition.</span></span>  
  
